105
00:06:47,670 --> 00:06:50,370
The person who was supposed to be in charge of the camera

106
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:52,870
was your subordinate in college,

107
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:53,970
but you forced your way to come here

108
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:54,970
