112
00:06:59,970 --> 00:07:03,570
to handle a live broadcast is him, you know!

113
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:05,970
I heard so, too.

114
00:07:05,970 --> 00:07:07,170
That advisor Suzuki went out of his way

115
00:07:07,170 --> 00:07:08,470
to get the children uniformed parkas,

116
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:10,170
and that he also wanted a person

117
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:12,270
who was at home at the camera for this job,

118
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,970
so he switched cameramen.

119
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:15,570
I went out of my way

120
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:17,870
only because the TV station told me that

121
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,270
