133
00:07:54,770 --> 00:07:56,170
It's true

134
00:07:56,170 --> 00:07:58,370
that if the phone call that the TV station received

135
00:07:58,370 --> 00:08:00,770
was from Thief Kid,

136
00:08:00,770 --> 00:08:02,470
he probably deliberately tried

137
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:05,770
to get rid of young people coming to this site.

138
00:08:05,770 --> 00:08:07,170
But, if so,

139
00:08:07,170 --> 00:08:11,270
why would he write something like that in postscript?

140
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:13,570
It's more than likely, judging from the personality of the advisor,

141
00:08:13,570 --> 00:08:16,970
that if something like that were to be written,

142
00:08:16,970 --> 00:08:18,970
he would most obviously call the Detective Squad over here.

143
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:23,670
But this case is full of mysteries.

144
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,270
It's strange that the treasure

145
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:28,370
