146
00:08:28,370 --> 00:08:30,570
but the same goes for the four keys

147
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:33,070
that the advisor nailed to the wall.

148
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:37,470
If he nailed the keys on only slightly...

