00:08:37,470 --> 00:08:39,070
After using the keys,

150
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:41,570
if the keys were to be nailed back on to the wall,

151
00:08:41,570 --> 00:08:44,570
the noise would be really loud.

152
00:08:44,570 --> 00:08:48,070
But there was no such sound in the video that we just watched.

153
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:51,170
Maybe the fluorescent paint on the keys and the keyholes

154
00:08:51,170 --> 00:08:52,470
