181
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:13,570
The white is the same as the red,

182
00:10:13,570 --> 00:10:15,370
and the card's right above the keyhole!

183
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:18,670
The card is more above by the black than the green!

184
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:23,970
I see. That's how it works.

185
00:10:23,970 --> 00:10:27,070
Okay. Will you surround my body

186
00:10:27,070 --> 00:10:29,270
