188
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:43,070
What we don't want to see will be exposed, too.

189
00:10:44,470 --> 00:10:47,170
No, that was just coincidence.

190
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:49,170
Dirty brat.

191
00:10:49,170 --> 00:10:50,970
Come off it, if I were really dirty,

192
00:10:50,970 --> 00:10:53,970
