221
00:12:39,717 --> 00:12:42,917
somewhere in this room where there are no accomplices.

222
00:12:42,917 --> 00:12:45,117
No accomplices?

223
00:12:45,117 --> 00:12:47,617
Hey, hey. Have you forgotten?

224
00:12:47,617 --> 00:12:49,117
You've got to insert the four keys

225
00:12:49,117 --> 00:12:51,317
into the four keyholes at the same time

226
00:12:51,317 --> 00:12:54,217
and turn the keys a the same time too, you know.

227
00:12:54,217 --> 00:12:56,817
There're going to have to be at least 4 of them all together

228
00:12:56,817 --> 00:12:58,517
including Kid to do it.

229
00:12:58,517 --> 00:13:01,217
And to begin with the four keys

230
00:13:01,217 --> 00:13:02,817
were fixed onto the wall like this

231
00:13:02,817 --> 00:13:06,017
by the old man before anything happened.

232
00:13:06,017 --> 00:13:08,417
The keys have nothing to do with what happened

233
00:13:08,417 --> 00:13:10,917
because Kid didn't use them!

234
00:13:10,917 --> 00:13:12,817
I told you, didn't I?

235
00:13:12,817 --> 00:13:17,317
That there was florescent paint on both the keys and the keyholes.

236
00:13:17,317 --> 00:13:21,317
But you don't know when the florescent paint was put there, do you?

237
00:13:21,317 --> 00:13:22,517
Right!

238
00:13:22,517 --> 00:13:26,817
Thief Kid could've put it on the keys and keyholes

239
00:13:26,817 --> 00:13:29,617
